{"tid":2026110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【豆腐沙中綫】斥調查幫政府港鐵 大判禮頓逍遙法外 「吹哨者」明入稟JR","createTime":"2020-05-20T17:36:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T23:53:31.000Z","uid":300722,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"724625705fe74628addf6d605d909372a8dd7bab","tid":2026110,"uid":300722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T17:36:13.000Z","msg":"港共狗鐵金翅仆街鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n港府就港鐵沙中綫紅磡站擴建工程醜聞成立獨立調查委員會，並於本月12日公開最終調查報告，狠批禮頓、港鐵及政府均要就工程失誤負責。被稱為沙中綫「吹哨者」的中科興業董事總經理潘焯鴻，早前已表明對報告不會「收貨」，並將於明天（21日）入稟高等法院，就調查委員會的最終報告申請司法覆核。<br />\n<br />\n獨立調查委員會的終極調查報告長達273頁，內容包括就剪短鋼筋及其他醜聞的調查結果，當中更狠批港鐵及禮頓雙方都有嚴重失誤，並認為政府須負上部份責任。潘焯鴻在報告出爐後已表明不會「收貨」，批評報告表面上是批評，實際是幫政府、港鐵及總承建商禮頓免卻民事及刑事責任，並不會放棄跟進事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200520/JFDDUOWYYWPMDXYFYX3PGSGARI/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200520%2FJFDDUOWYYWPMDXYFYX3PGSGARI%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsfUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=955cf86e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200520%2FJFDDUOWYYWPMDXYFYX3PGSGARI%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=53264596\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200520/JFDDUOWYYWPMDXYFYX3PGSGARI/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"bdfb503a007b4723a232f02ec89116ddb868adad","tid":2026110,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T23:53:31.000Z","msg":"因為港共黨鐵都身有屎"}]}